text: Kelley Jones (born December 8, 1965) is an American rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:American female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Houston
